## GOG Game Downloader

Cross-platform desktop app for browsing your owned GOG titles, managing download jobs, and configuring storage/settings.

## Implemented phases

- Foundation (UI shell + sidebar + themed pages)
- Authentication (OAuth PKCE + token persistence)
- Library UX (game list load and search)
- Downloads phase wiring (pause/resume active jobs via service)
- Storage phase wiring (drive enumeration + primary/backup detection)
- Data/settings phase wiring (SQLite-backed app settings persistence)

## Build

Requires .NET SDK 10.0 or newer.

```bash
dotnet build /absolute/path/to/gog-game-downloader/src/GogGameDownloader.csproj
```

## Setup and install scripts

Scripts are under `/absolute/path/to/gog-game-downloader/scripts`.

### Linux

1. `bash /absolute/path/to/gog-game-downloader/scripts/setup-linux.sh`
2. `bash /absolute/path/to/gog-game-downloader/scripts/install-linux.sh`
3. Run `gog-game-downloader`

### Windows (PowerShell)

1. `powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File C:\path\to\gog-game-downloader\scripts\setup-windows.ps1`
2. `powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File C:\path\to\gog-game-downloader\scripts\install-windows.ps1`
3. Launch **GOG Game Downloader** from the Start Menu
